## âš™ï¸ How to Run Project Locally

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Clone Repo
```sh
git clone https://github.com/AnanthaMahadevan0603/ecommerce-backend.git
cd ecommerce-backend

2ï¸âƒ£ Configure MySQL (application.properties)
spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/ecommerce
spring.datasource.username=YOUR_MYSQL_USER
spring.datasource.password=YOUR_MYSQL_PASSWORD
spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update

jwt.secret=YOUR_SECRET_KEY
jwt.expiration=86400000

3ï¸âƒ£ Run the Project

From terminal:

mvn spring-boot:run


OR from Eclipse:
â¡ Right click project â†’ Run As â†’ Spring Boot App

ğŸ§ª API Endpoints (Main)
Auth APIs
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/api/auth/register	Register new user
POST	/api/auth/login	Login + get JWT
Product APIs
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/api/products	Add product (ADMIN)
GET	/api/products	List products (pagination/filter)
PUT	/api/products/{id}	Update product
DELETE	/api/products/{id}	Delete product
Cart APIs
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/api/cart/add	Add item
PUT	/api/cart/update	Update quantity
DELETE	/api/cart/remove/{id}	Remove item
GET	/api/cart	View cart
Order APIs
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/api/orders	Place order
GET	/api/orders	User order history
GET	/api/orders/all	Admin: all orders
ğŸ“¦ Database Diagram (Simplified)
User (1) ----- (Many) Orders
User (1) ----- (One) Cart
Cart (1) ----- (Many) CartItems
Order (1) ---- (Many) OrderItems
Product (1) -- (Many) CartItems
Product (1) -- (Many) OrderItems
User (Many) -- (Many) Role

